      <title>欧洲央行和英国央行不愿与美联储一起转向降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/fed-leads-way-toward-rate-cuts-as-europeans-fret-on-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长并不急于加入美国转向降息的行列——尽管投资者一直坚称他们需要尽快采取更宽松的货币政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/fed-leads-way-toward-rate-cuts-as-europeans-fret-on-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 18:01:05 GMT</pubDate>
